{"id": "art-454", "label": "Art. 454", "title": "Art. 454: Procedura adopţiei", "slug": "art-454", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 454: Procedura adop&#355;iei </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)Adop&#355;ia se\nîncuviin&#355;eaz&#259; de c&#259;tre instan&#355;a de tutel&#259;, dac&#259;\neste în interesul superior al copilului &#351;i sunt îndeplinite toate\ncelelalte condi&#355;ii prev&#259;zute de lege.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)Procedura adop&#355;iei este\nreglementat&#259; prin lege special&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'><span style='color:black'>SEC&#354;IUNEA 2:Condi&#355;iile de fond ale\nadop&#355;iei</span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'><span style='color:black'>SUBSEC&#354;IUNEA 1:Persoanele care pot fi\nadoptate</span></b></p>"}